title: King David's
typeOfFood: Lacto, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Adjacent to Syracuse University and a city fixture since 1974, this upstairs restaurant serves many of the familiar Greek & Middle-East items, as well as deep-fried eggplant and asparagus. Order at the counter and then the food is brought to you.
